label_description: I am a 30-year-old person, honest, proactive, and constantly adapting and learning. I am passionate about continuous growth, both personally and professionally. Personally, I believe that healthy eating and sports are essential in my daily life. I practice CrossFit every day, which not only helps me stay physically fit but also allows me to manage my mind better, facing challenges with clarity and energy. I also have a dog who is my inseparable companion and joins me on all my adventures, always bringing joy and companionship to my daily life.
